ribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:16:\"Customize AIOSEO\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:15:\"WPCode snippets\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:28:\"https://aioseo.com/?p=197966\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:478:\"<p>Would you like to customize All in One SEO (AIOSEO)? Our world-class engineers have created code snippets that do just that. Until now, this custom code wasn&#8217;t available to the public. But thanks to the new integration with WPCode, you&#8230;</p>\nThe post <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-use-the-wpcode-snippet-library/\">How to Use the New AIOSEO Code Library (WPCode Integration) – WordPress Tutorial</a> first appeared on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com\">AIOSEO</a>.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:15:\"Sherrie Gossett\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:15189:\"<p>Would you like to customize All in One SEO (AIOSEO)? Our world-class engineers have created code snippets that do just that.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Until now, this custom code wasn&#8217;t available to the public. But thanks to the new integration with WPCode, you can now customize AIOSEO with a few button clicks.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>In this tutorial, you&#8217;ll learn how to use this new snippet library to add new functionality to AIOSEO.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"is-layout-flow wp-block-group aioseo-table-of-contents has-theme-info-background-color has-background\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>In This Article</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-aioseo-table-of-contents\"><ul><li><a href=\"#aioseo-step-1-download-all-in-one-seo-aioseo\">Step 1: Download All in One SEO (AIOSEO)</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-step-2-navigate-to-the-code-snippet-library\">Step 2: Go to the Code Snippet Library</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-step-3-activate-a-snippet\">Step 3: Activate a Snippet</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-insertion-options\">Optional: Customize Insertion</a><ul></ul></li></ul></div>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-step-1-download-all-in-one-seo-aioseo\">Step 1: Download All in One SEO (AIOSEO)</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>First, if you haven’t done so already, <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/pricing/\" title=\"\">download</a> and <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/docs/installing-all-in-one-seo-pro/\" title=\"\">install</a> All in One SEO.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>All in One SEO (AIOSEO) is an established plugin with thousands of 5-star ratings on WordPress.org and over 3 million users.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>After you’ve uploaded the plugin to your WordPress site, a setup wizard will open and walk you through a few steps.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"485\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-homepage-1024x485.png\" alt=\"aioseo homepage\" class=\"wp-image-140989\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-homepage-1024x485.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-homepage-300x142.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-homepage-768x364.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-homepage-600x284.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-homepage-127x60.png 127w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-homepage-190x90.png 190w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-homepage.png 1260w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-step-2-navigate-to-the-code-snippet-library\">Step 2: Navigate to the Code Snippet Library</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Next, in the WordPress admin bar, go to <strong>AIOSEO </strong><strong>»</strong><strong> Tools </strong><strong>» Code Snippets</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you don’t already have WPCode installed, you’ll see a prompt to install it. You can <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/insert-headers-and-footers/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">get the plugin for free</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Now, in AIOSEO, you’ll see the code snippets.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"616\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/aioseo-code-snippets-1024x616.png\" alt=\"aioseo code snippets\" class=\"wp-image-197984\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/aioseo-code-snippets-1024x616.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/aioseo-code-snippets-300x180.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/aioseo-code-snippets-768x462.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/aioseo-code-snippets-1536x924.png 1536w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/aioseo-code-snippets-2048x1232.png 2048w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/aioseo-code-snippets-600x361.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/aioseo-code-snippets-100x60.png 100w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/aioseo-code-snippets-150x90.png 150w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Currently, there are <em>14 code snippets</em> to choose from.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>For our tutorial, we’ll choose <strong>Limit Meta Description to 160 Characters.</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>This code snippet truncates your meta descriptions, site-wide, to 160 characters. It does this in the HTML code of each web page.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>To get started, click the blue <strong>Use Snippet</strong> button. That will open a new window.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"322\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/aioseo-wpcode-meta-desription-code-snippet-1024x322.png\" alt=\"aioseo meta description code snippet\" class=\"wp-image-198070\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/aioseo-wpcode-meta-desription-code-snippet-1024x322.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/aioseo-wpcode-meta-desription-code-snippet-300x94.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/aioseo-wpcode-meta-desription-code-snippet-768x241.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/aioseo-wpcode-meta-desription-code-snippet-600x189.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/aioseo-wpcode-meta-desription-code-snippet-190x60.png 190w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/aioseo-wpcode-meta-desription-code-snippet-286x90.png 286w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/aioseo-wpcode-meta-desription-code-snippet.png 1368w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-step-3-activate-a-snippet\">Step 3: Activate a Snippet</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Now, in the upper right,</p>\n\n\n\n<ol>\n<li>Toggle the Inactive button to <strong>Active.</strong></li>\n\n\n\n<li>Click <strong>Update</strong>.</li>\n</ol>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/wpcode-aioseo-meta-description-code-snippet-1024x427.png\" alt=\"activate aioseo meta description code snippet\" class=\"wp-image-197987\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/wpcode-aioseo-meta-description-code-snippet-1024x427.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/wpcode-aioseo-meta-description-code-snippet-300x125.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/wpcode-aioseo-meta-description-code-snippet-768x320.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/wpcode-aioseo-meta-description-code-snippet-1536x640.png 1536w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/wpcode-aioseo-meta-description-code-snippet-2048x854.png 2048w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/wpcode-aioseo-meta-description-code-snippet-600x250.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/wpcode-aioseo-meta-description-code-snippet-144x60.png 144w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/wpcode-aioseo-meta-description-code-snippet-216x90.png 216w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>That’s all you need to do. The code snippet is now active.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>To <em>deactivate</em> a code snippet, simply toggle the button back to <strong>Inactive</strong> and click the blue <strong>Update</strong> button again.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The AIOSEO team will continue to add more snippets to the library.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-insertion-options\">Optional: Customize Insertion</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The default insertion for the code snippet is for it to be automatically inserted (&#8220;Auto Insert) on all pages (&#8220;Run Everywhere&#8221;) and all device types. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"658\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/aioseo-edit-code-snippet-1024x658.png\" alt=\"edit aioseo code snippet\" class=\"wp-image-198090\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/aioseo-edit-code-snippet-1024x658.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/aioseo-edit-code-snippet-300x193.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/aioseo-edit-code-snippet-768x493.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/aioseo-edit-code-snippet-1536x987.png 1536w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/aioseo-edit-code-snippet-2048x1316.png 2048w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/aioseo-edit-code-snippet-600x385.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/aioseo-edit-code-snippet-93x60.png 93w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/aioseo-edit-code-snippet-140x90.png 140w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The default settings will meet most users&#8217; needs. But you can customize these settings.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Insert Method</strong>: Instead of <strong>Auto Insert</strong> you can choose <strong>Shortcode</strong> to add the snippet manually to select pages. </p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Location</strong>: If you choose Auto Insert, you&#8217;ll get a variety of options to choose from in the Location drop-down. These include</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Front-end only</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Admin only</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Site-wide header, footer, or body</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>You can also choose the location based on HTML elements and CSS selectors if you&#8217;re using <a href=\"https://library.wpcode.com/pricing\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" title=\"\">WPCode&#8217;s Pro Version</a>. </p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Schedule snippet</strong>: You can also use a <em>date picker</em> to schedule the snippet to run for a <em>specified time frame</em>. (Requires WPCode Pro.)</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Device types</strong>: Scroll down a bit further in the window and you&#8217;ll see an option to limit the device types your code snippet will be active on.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"419\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/aioseo-code-snippet-device-type-options-1024x419.png\" alt=\"aioseo code snippets device type options\" class=\"wp-image-198097\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/aioseo-code-snippet-device-type-options-1024x419.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/aioseo-code-snippet-device-type-options-300x123.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/aioseo-code-snippet-device-type-options-768x315.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/aioseo-code-snippet-device-type-options-600x246.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/aioseo-code-snippet-device-type-options-147x60.png 147w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/aioseo-code-snippet-device-type-options-220x90.png 220w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/aioseo-code-snippet-device-type-options.png 1282w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Smart conditional logic</strong>: You can also choose to show or hide your code snippet on pages based on conditions, like</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>The page URL</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Whether a user is logged in </li>\n\n\n\n<li>The user&#8217;s role</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Type of page (Post type, Referrer, etc.)</li>\n\n\n\n<li>WooCommerce page</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Easy Digital Downloads page</li>\n\n\n\n<li>MemberPress page</li>\n\n\n\n<li>and more.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"515\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/aioseo-code-snippets-conditional-logic-1024x515.png\" alt=\"aioseo code snippets conditional logic\" class=\"wp-image-198102\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/aioseo-code-snippets-conditional-logic-1024x515.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/aioseo-code-snippets-conditional-logic-300x151.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/aioseo-code-snippets-conditional-logic-768x386.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/aioseo-code-snippets-conditional-logic-1536x772.png 1536w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/aioseo-code-snippets-conditional-logic-2048x1029.png 2048w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/aioseo-code-snippets-conditional-logic-600x302.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/aioseo-code-snippets-conditional-logic-119x60.png 119w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/aioseo-code-snippets-conditional-logic-179x90.png 179w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-how-to-access-aioseo-code-snippets-in-wpcode\">How to Access AIOSEO Code Snippets in WPCode</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>You can also access our code snippets directly from WPCode.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you have <a href=\"https://wpcode.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" title=\"\">WPCode</a> installed, go to <strong>WPCode</strong> <strong>» Library.</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>You’ll see a button at the bottom left for AIOSEO’s code snippets.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/aioseo-wpcode-integration-693x1024.png\" alt=\"wpcode menu aioseo item\" class=\"wp-image-193996\" width=\"347\" height=\"512\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/aioseo-wpcode-integration-693x1024.png 693w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/aioseo-wpcode-integration-203x300.png 203w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/aioseo-wpcode-integration-768x1135.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/aioseo-wpcode-integration-1039x1536.png 1039w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/aioseo-wpcode-integration-600x887.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/aioseo-wpcode-integration-41x60.png 41w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/aioseo-wpcode-integration-61x90.png 61w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/aioseo-wpcode-integration.png 1242w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 347px) 100vw, 347px\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\"><em>When you open </em><strong><em>WPCode</em></strong><em>, look under </em><strong><em>Library</em></strong><em> to see </em><strong><em>AIOSEO</em></strong><em> as a menu item. (Enlarged here.)</em></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-whats-next\">What’s Next?</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This post helped you understand how to use the new WP Code integration.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Next, explore how to <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/breadcrumb-navigation-in-wordpress/\">add breadcrumb navigation</a> in WordPress and learn how to turn your web pages into <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-add-rich-snippets-to-wordpress/\">rich snippets</a>. And don&#8217;t forget to <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/lead-generation/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" title=\"\">capture leads</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you found this article helpful, please subscribe to our <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/c/AIOSEO\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">YouTube Channel</a>. You’ll find many more helpful tutorials there. You can also follow us on <a href=\"https://twitter.com/aioseopack\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">Twitter</a>, <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/company/aioseo/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">LinkedIn</a>, or <a href=\"https://facebook.com/aioseopack/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">Facebook</a> to stay in the loop.</p>The post <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-use-the-wpcode-snippet-library/\">How to Use the New AIOSEO Code Library (WPCode Integration) – WordPress Tutorial</a> first appeared on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com\">AIOSEO</a>.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:62:\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-use-the-wpcode-snippet-library/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:8;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:88:\"\n		\n		\n					\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n					\n										\n					\n	